headline: Extra Space Storage: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The Salt Lake City-based real estate investment trust said it had funds from operations of $460.8 million, or $2.08 per share, in the period. The average estimate of six analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $2.03 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.
